---
By: Han Shan
Source:
  ISBN: 1556591403
  Locus:
    Page: 255
  Publisher: Copper Canyon Press
  Title: The Collected Songs of Cold Mountain
  Translator: Red Pine
---
Cold Mountain's remoteness
suits my mind
pure white rocks
no yellow gold
the echo of a spring
the sound of Po-ya's zither
if Tzu-ch'i were here
he would know the tune
